Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別學小孩子那樣高喊「出發」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情好像不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在還在修煉中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉不是還有第三階段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛剛完成了第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三階段可以邊走邊修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個普通的氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一階段是旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二階段是威力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波紋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這個」到底是怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表怎麼看都是個普通的氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼看 就是個普通的氣球嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我用左手把同樣的動作再演示一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣球的裡面到底是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 查克拉亂旋轉的速度越來越快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呈一個漂亮的圓形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手握著的氣球 內部也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓查克拉如此劇烈的旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但氣球卻如同靜止一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比弄破這個氣球時的威力更大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉的旋轉也更劇烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將前兩個階段所學的全部發揮出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將查克拉的旋轉和威力都發揮到極限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時在氣球內部形成一個內膜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後將查克拉壓縮在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是將前兩個階段\N的所學發揮到極限的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能讓氣球破裂的修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都沒見你這麼聰明過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼非要特地做這種修煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設修煉的第二階段成果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 如果掌握第三階段後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把這個小颱風維持在手掌裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就不會分散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉逐漸加快 威力逐漸被壓縮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的破壞力就會積蓄至最大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以抑制自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將旋轉和威力發揮到極限
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後將之維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能真正地完全控制自己的力量之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒法做到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於明白了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比前兩個階段難多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就說過 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是A級學習難度的超高等忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 說明到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊走邊練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說 也不必那麼急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體恢復需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒準到時綱手就不在鎮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她遇到老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也肯定不會留下敘舊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我找得好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是來和我敘舊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我有一個小小的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳很亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看臉色 他燒得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直處於疲勞狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信您應該已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找別人吧 我已經不再治療了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該知道這傷勢有多麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人可以治癒這個傷勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享有醫療專家的美稱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的三忍 綱手公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了您之外 沒人可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手 不是普通的傷勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是特殊的咒印之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我在殺第三代時受的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別擺出那麼可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有形的東西早晚要凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你應該也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你也害死了自己最愛的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最愛的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的想法真是殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們死得太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想置我們於死地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的手下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該非常瞭解我的個性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定還是單身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手性子急 脾氣又暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 現在不是頑皮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個野女人又不知道跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你對一個\N刻苦努力的徒弟所說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起你 現在找綱手更優先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人專程尋訪的那個叫綱手女忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是個什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願她還在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是來打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想和你們做筆交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才已經說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治癒大蛇丸大人手臂的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不打算讓您白干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一筆交易如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數到五
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就幹掉你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對您來說 說不定是個好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說讓你所愛的弟弟和那個男人復活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我發明的禁忌之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就說明交易…成功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大姐我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說要去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺回在這裡輸掉的淺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉 威力 然後將它們發揮到極限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後將它們維持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那裡」是指哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個骰子的點數之和 偶為「丁」 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇為「半」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 這裡可是賭場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擺弄那個氣球了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒空玩那個骰子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無聊的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭場裡可沒有免費的交易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏的話 情報免費 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了就付一千兩 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 選丁還是半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年正好50歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是半的話 我就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二和五 是半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千兩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該去哪兒找好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 四處都沒看到蹤影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大人小孩都喜歡的很有趣的彩票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有當場開獎的 要不要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是胖乎乎的樣子可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到只買一張彩票就中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙看來很有賭博的天賦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然忍術的才能遜人一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 綱手到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從時間上來看 應該不會走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到高處找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鎮子好像是座城下街
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先得攀上城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想見他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩樹 斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果治好你的手 你打算幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不喜歡撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如實告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說 哪裡有城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我想得到的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 我還要徹底毀滅木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼傳說中的女忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼醫療專家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她來做下任火影 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個在我面前看不起第三代爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第四代的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你是不是第五代候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會給你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:22:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒爆發 不可饒恕
